ifferent-china-douyin-jonathan-haidt-anxious-generation-national-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20losing%20countless%20hours%20of%20productivity%20to%2030-second%20clips%20of%20soup%20recipes%20I've%20yet%20to%20make%2C%20hair-growing%20products%20I've%20yet%20to%20buy%2C%20and%20gua%20sha%20tutorials%20I'll%20likely%20never%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETired%20of%20spending%20my%20one%20wild%20and%20precious%20life%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparent-screen-time-rules-kids-benefited-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estaring%20at%20a%20screen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20change%20in%202025.%20And%20thanks%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgetbrick.app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrick%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20%2459%20gadget%20designed%20to%20block%20phone%20apps%2C%20I've%20actually%20been%20able%20to%20follow%20through%20with%20this%20New%20Year's%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d93ddb7-2096-4590-8bdc-a2f1de01dcf9%5C%22%3EA%20physical%20key%20to%20becoming%20distraction-free%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Using%20the%20Brick%20gadget%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b3f6cb6630eb10385cd56f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20only%20unblock%20the%20apps%20on%20your%20phone%20by%20tapping%20the%20Brick%20key.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20weekly%20screen%20time%20report%20became%20increasingly%20alarming%20last%20year%2C%20I%20attempted%20to%20fight%20back%20by%20setting%20a%20daily%20one-hour%20limit%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fditched-doomscrolling-instagram-decluttered-my-feed-took-one-year-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20TikTok%20on%20my%20iPhone.%20But%20when%20I%20realized%20the%20limit%20could%20be%20bypassed%20with%20the%20click%20of%20a%20button%2C%20the%20software%20was%20quickly%20rendered%20completely%20useless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20same%20struggle%20is%20what%20led%20recent%20college%20graduates%20TJ%20Driver%20and%20Zach%20Nasgowitz%20to%20create%20Brick%2C%20which%20allows%20you%20to%20temporarily%20block%20chosen%20apps%20and%20their%20notifications%20via%20a%20physical%20device%20that%20comes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%203D-printed%202-inch%20by%202-inch%20square%20magnet.%20You%20can%20still%20access%20whatever%20apps%20you%20need%20throughout%20the%20day%20%E2%80%94%20like%20texts%2C%20photos%2C%20or%20Google%20Maps%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Brick%20makes%20it%20harder%20to%20give%20into%20the%20temptation%20of%20a%20quick%20social%20media%20dopamine%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20other%20solutions%2C%20the%20'key'%20that%20re-enables%20distractions%20is%20always%20present%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Brick%20website%20explains.%20%26quot%3BBrick%20allows%20you%20to%20leave%20that%20key%20behind%2C%20turning%20your%20phone%20into%20a%20new%2C%20distraction-free%20device%20until%20you%20return.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e32edce4-02b7-4815-a1f0-2619ec863859%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20Brick%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20Brick%20couldn't%20be%20simpler.%20After%20downloading%20the%20corresponding%20app%20and%20creating%20a%20Brick%20account%20with%20my%20email%2C%20I%20activated%20my%20Brick%20by%20tapping%20the%20top%20of%20my%20phone%20on%20the%20lightweight%20square.%20A%20single%20Brick%20can%20be%20used%20with%20multiple%20iPhones%20%E2%80%94%20unlike%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-benefitting-from-password-crackdown-good-for-disney-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there's%20no%20limit%20%E2%80%94%20so%20my%20boyfriend%20was%20able%20to%20connect%20his%20iPhone%20to%20it%20as%20well%20(Brick%20is%20currently%20not%20available%20for%20Android%20users).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20then%20prompted%20to%20allow%20screen%20time%20access%20to%20Brick%2C%20which%20gives%20it%20the%20ability%20to%20block%20and%20unblock%20apps%20on%20the%20iPhones%2C%20and%20create%20my%20first%20%26quot%3BMode.%26quot%3B%20You%20can%20create%20different%20modes%20to%20block%20different%20apps.%20I%20made%20one%20titled%20%26quot%3BGet%20to%20work!%26quot%3B%20and%20chose%20to%20block%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%2C%20TikTok%2C%20and%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20activate%20these%20modes%20through%20the%20app%20or%20by%20physically%20tapping%20your%20phone%20on%20the%20square.%20But%20you%20can%20only%20deactivate%20the%20block%20by%20tapping%20your%20phone%20against%20the%20Brick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202235b8c-5bbd-4c9a-8445-5d8f170f7813%5C%22%3EA%20swift%20change%20in%20habits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Brick%20warning%20message%20when%20you%20try%20to%20access%20a%20blocked%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b3f73b6630eb10385cd57c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Brick%20warning%20message%20when%20you%20try%20to%20access%20a%20blocked%20app.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20very%20first%20day%20I%20used%20Brick%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20how%20hooked%20I'd%20become%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteens-dont-have-social-media-accounts-not-allowed-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20caught%20myself%20unconsciously%20picking%20up%20my%20phone%20multiple%20times%20an%20hour%20to%20check%20Instagram%20or%20TikTok.%20It%20was%20a%20major%20wake-up%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20became%20diligent%20about%20tapping%20my%20phone%20to%20the%20little%20Brick%