he%20appointment%20of%20the%20Raigad%20and%20Nashik%20guardian%20ministers%2C%20had%20recently%20been%20accommodated%20in%20the%20State%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20by%20modifying%20rules%20after%20he%20was%20unhappy%20over%20being%20left%20out%20of%20it.%20As%20chief%20minister%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20heads%20the%20authority%20while%20his%20other%20deputy%20and%20NCP%20chief%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20also%20part%20of%20it%20because%20he%20holds%20the%20finance%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20cabinet%20changed%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20panel%20to%20include%20the%20post%20of%20'deputy%20chief%20minister'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20is%20reportedly%20not%20well%20between%20Mr%20Shinde%20and%20Mr%20Pawar%20either%20since%20the%20government%20decided%20not%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20appointment%20of%20NCP%20leader%20Aditi%20Tatkare%20and%20the%20BJP's%20Girish%20Mahajan%20as%20the%20guardian%20ministers%20of%20Nashik%20and%20Raigad.%20From%20the%20Sena%2C%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme%20Minister%20Bharatseth%20Gogawale%20and%20School%20Education%20Minister%20Dadaji%20Bhuse%20wanted%20to%20be%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20districts%2C%20especially%20because%20Nashik%20will%20be%20hosting%20the%20Kumbh%20Mela%20in%202027.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20had%20also%20skipped%20a%20review%20meeting%20for%20the%20Kumbh%20Mela%20chaired%20by%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20held%20one%20of%20his%20own%20a%20few%20days%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20Resentment'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20perceived%20troubles%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Mahayuti%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BMahayuti%20celebrating%20valentine%20month.%20Not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20IT%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Ashish%20Shelar%20insisted%20that%20there%20are%20no%20differences%20within%20the%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20resentment%2C%20everything%20is%20going%20well%20in%20Mahayuti%2C%20all%20this%20is%20just%20a%20pipe%20dream.%20Chief%20Minister%20Fadnavis%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20Shinde%20and%20Pawar%20are%20running%20the%20government%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739877480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F9ko7rkcg_devendra-fadnavis-eknath-shinde-ajit-pawar-fadanvis-shinde-ajit_625x300_11_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiv-sena-bjp-ncp-eknath-shinde-mahayuti-security-cover-withdrawn-maharashtra-ruling-alliance-rift-widens-sources-say-latest-flashpoint-is-7737995%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Less%20than%20three%20months%20after%20it%20won%20the%20Maharashtra%20elections%20by%20a%20landslide%2C%20the%20rift%20within%20the%20ruling%20BJP-Shiv%20Sena-NCP%20alliance%20seems%20to%20be%20widening%20with%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20'Y'-security%20cover%20to%20some%20MLAs%20emerging%20as%20the%20latest%20flashpoint.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiv-sena-bjp-ncp-eknath-shinde-mahayuti-security-cover-withdrawn-maharashtra-ruling-alliance-rift-widens-sources-say-latest-flashpoint-is-7737995%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BTS%20Jin%20crowned%20as%20most%20handsome%20Kpop%20Idol%20of%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739877460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118357118%2Cimgsize-26920.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fbts-jin-takes-the-crown-as-most-handsome-kpop-idol-of-2024-read-here%2Farticleshow%2F118357148.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22htt