hat%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20enforced%20in%20the%20state%20violated%20his%20personal%20liberty%20and%20privacy.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20secret%3F%20Both%20of%20you%20are%20living%20together%3B%20your%20neighbor%20knows%2C%20society%20knows%2C%20and%20the%20world%20knows.%20Then%20where%20is%20the%20secrecy%20you%20are%20talking%20about%3F...What%20gossip%3F%20Are%20you%20living%20secretly%2C%20in%20some%20secluded%20cave%3F%20You%20are%20living%20amongst%20civil%20society.%20What%20is%20the%20privacy%20that%20is%20invaded%3F%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20G%20Narendar%20and%20Justice%20Alok%20Mahra%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fbrazenly-living-without-marriage-uttarakhand-high-court-privacy-concern-ucc-challenge%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20plea%2C%20Jai%20Tripathi%20had%20challenged%20specific%20provisions%20under%20the%20UCC%2C%20including%20the%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships.%20He%20said%20the%20provision%20%26quot%3Binstitutionalised%20gossip%20and%20intruded%20on%20personal%20choices%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20state%20government%20is%20not%20prohibiting%20live-in%20relationships%20but%20is%20merely%20providing%20for%20their%20registration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20hasn't%20said%20that%20you%20can't%20live%20together...%20Who%20is%20coming%20in%20between%3F%20You%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20you%20are%20alleging%20that%20they%20are%20invading%20your%20privacy%2C%20disclosing%20your%20details.%20If%20there%20is%20any%20such%20material%2C%20please%20disclose%20it.%20No%20omnibus%20submissions.%20If%20you%20make%20allegations%2C%20be%20specific%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20further%20remarked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2027%2C%20Uttarakhand%20became%20the%20first%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20enact%20%C2%A0the%20UCC%2C%20laying%20a%20framework%20for%20uniform%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20property%2C%20inheritance%20and%20adoption%20laws%20for%20all%20the%20citizens.%20Among%20the%20clauses%20is%20the%20mandatory%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20and%20parental%20consent%20for%20live-in%20relationships%20involving%20individuals%20under%2021%20years%20of%20age.%20The%20rule%20will%20apply%20to%20%26quot%3Bany%20resident%20of%20Uttarakhand...%20in%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20outside%20the%20state%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFailure%20to%20declare%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20or%20providing%20false%20information%2C%20could%20attract%20imprisonment%20for%20three%20months%20or%20attract%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20or%20both.%20Even%20a%20month's%20delay%20in%20registration%20could%20trigger%20a%20prison%20term%20of%20up%20to%20three%20months%2C%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%20or%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20also%20recognises%20children%20born%20out%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Blegitimate%20child%20of%20the%20couple%26quot%3B%20and%20ensures%20equal%20rights%20for%20them%20in%20inheritance.%20Both%20sons%20and%20daughters%20will%20be%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bchild%26quot%3B%2C%20omitting%20any%20gender%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20online%20portal%20has%20been%20launched%20by%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20to%20register%20marriages%2C%20divorces%2C%20succession%20rights%2C%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20and%20their%20termination.%20These%20processes%20can%20be%20carried%20out%20from%20mobile%20phones%20or%20desktops%20and%20the%20progress%20of%20applications%20can%20be%20checked%20through%20email%20or%20SMS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20law%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20offering%20made%20by%20our%20state%20in%20the%20great%20'yagya'%20being%20performed%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20make%20the%20country%20a%20developed%2C%20organised%2C%20harmonious%20and%20self-reliant%20nation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739877000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F2fjd9u7o_live-in-relationship-_625x300_30_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-high-court-uniform-civil-code-live-in-relationship-law-couples-registration-privacy-7738353%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Uttarakhand%20High%20Court%20has%20taken%20strong%20exception%20to%20a%20petition%20that%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20enforced%20in%20the%20state%20violated%20personal%20liberty%20and%20privacy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-high-court-uniform-civil-code-live-in-relationship-law-couples-registration-privacy-7738353%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20iPhone%20SE%20set%20to%20launch%20on%20February%2019%3A%20Check%20top%205%20expected%20upgrades%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739876984000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fapple-iphone-se-set-to-launch-on-february-19-check-top-5-expected-upgrades-125021800677_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20Apple%20iPhone%20SE%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20powered%20by%20the%20A18%20chip%2C%20enabling%20support%20for%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Everyone%20must%20go'%3A%20New%20Zealand%20tourism%20campaign%20criticised%20as%20tone%20deaf%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739876940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F02%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-new-zealand-tou