%20organizations%20not%20to%20complete%20current%20applications.%20This%20is%20especially%20devastating%20for%20us.%20We%20don't%20know%20if%20and%20when%20they'll%20repost%20notices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4a7e8c1-38ed-4338-80ec-2b209b8839ce%5C%22%3EWe%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20plan%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20should%20be%20able%20to%20trust%20our%20government%20to%20honor%20its%20commitments%2C%20but%20right%20now%2C%20we're%20still%20waiting%20to%20see%20what%20happens%20with%20most%20of%20our%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20our%20annual%20conference%20on%20hold.%20We'd%20typically%20be%20confirming%20presenters%20and%20workshop%20topics%20now%2C%20including%20workshops%20on%20how%20to%20work%20with%20specific%20populations%2C%20such%20as%20survivors%20who%20are%20deaf%20or%20hard%20of%20hearing.%20With%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-targets-dei-mandates-federal-employees-day-one-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20DEI%20restrictions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20don't%20know%20if%20we're%20even%20allowed%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20don't%20know%20if%20our%20members%20and%20partners%20will%20be%20able%20to%20use%20their%20grant%20funds%20to%20attend%20the%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20on%20the%20hook%20with%20a%20hotel%20contract%2C%20and%20if%20we%20cancel%2C%20it'll%20cost%20us%20about%20%2422%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd5260d8-240c-4de7-b2cf-208d1d5099f9%5C%22%3EI'm%20worried%20what%20this%20means%20for%20our%20staff%20and%20the%20survivors%20we%20support%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20very%20difficult%20to%20support%20a%20survivor%20who's%20in%20a%20crisis%20or%20navigating%20very%20complex%20systems%20when%20you%20yourself%20are%20in%20a%20crisis%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-worried-about-job-loss-getting-fired-during-recession-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworried%20about%20your%20job%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2011%2C%20we%20received%20communication%20from%20the%20CDC%20that%20it%20rescinded%20its%20memos%20to%20cease%20DEI%20activities%20on%20all%20CDC-funded%20awards%20and%20cease%20all%20activities%20promoting%20gender%20ideology.%20If%20we%20continue%20to%20receive%20similar%20communication%2C%20we'll%20resume%20all%20activities%20as%20normal%20and%20hope%20to%20continue%20to%20be%20reimbursed%20for%20our%20current%20grant%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20leader%2C%20I'm%20making%20sure%20I'm%20not%20bearing%20the%20weight%20of%20what%20is%20going%20on%20alone%20by%20keeping%20staff%20informed%2C%20asking%20for%20their%20input%2C%20and%20having%20conversations%20with%20other%20leaders%20for%20support%20and%20ideas.%20Being%20in%20a%20community%20with%20our%20organization%2C%20members%2C%20and%20partners%20is%20helping%20me%20cope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20your%20business%20or%20organization%20relies%20on%20federal%20funding%20and%20you%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20please%20email%20Manseen%20Logan%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amlogan%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emlogan%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnonprofit-director-stressed-about-federal-funding-how-to-cope-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739873221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ae6c60eb4be2fff9a4a08b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnonprofit-director-stressed-about-federal-funding-how-to-cope-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brie%20Franklin's%20nonprofit%20receives%2090%25%20of%20its%20funding%20from%20federal%20grants%20and%20is%20uncertain%20about%20the%20future.%20Her%20community%20is%20helping%20her%20to%20cope.%2