ing%20this%20(the%20threats).%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20State%20will%20provide%20necessary%20protection...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20finally%2C%20also%20accepted%20Mr%20Allahbadia's%20submissions%2C%20giving%20him%20temporary%20protection%20from%20arrest%20and%20blocking%20further%20police%20cases%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolice%20Cases%2C%20Death%20Threats%20For%20'BeerBiceps%20Guy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanveer%20Allahbadia%20faces%20not%20only%20multiple%20police%20cases%20but%20also%20a%20summons%20from%20the%20National%20Commission%20of%20Women%20(on%20March%206%2C%20after%20skipping%20one%20for%20Monday%2C%20citing%20the%20death%20threats%20and%20a%20Rs%205%20lakh%20bounty%20on%20his%20head)%20and%2C%20possibly%2C%20questions%20from%20a%20parliamentary%20panel%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20others%20-%20show%20host%20Samay%20Raima%20and%20participant%20Apoorva%20Makhija%20-%20also%20reported%20threats%3B%20both%20are%20named%20in%20police%20cases%2C%20as%20has%20Ashish%20Chanchalani%2C%20another%20social%20media%20influencer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20Mr%20Allahbadia%20confessed%20to%20feeling%20%26quot%3Bscared%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20threats%20to%20his%20life%20but%20insisted%20he%20would%20not%20back%20down.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20watching%20death%20threats%20pour%20in%20from%20people%20saying%20they%20want%20to%20kill%20me...%20hurt%20my%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20also%20claiming%20an%20'invasion'%20of%20his%20mother's%20medical%20clinic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-running-away-ranveer-allahbadias-new-post-amid-crass-remarks-row-7718534%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BScared%2C%20But%20Not%20Running%26quot%3B%3A%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia's%20New%20Post%20Amid%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20failed%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20cops%2C%20cops%20from