nicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2k2ly8j75o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2k2ly8j75o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2k2ly8j75o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20and%20Musk%20froze%20USAID%20funding%20to%20put%20Americans%20first.%20US%20citizens%20are%20feeling%20the%20impact.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20worker%20removes%20the%20U.S.%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20sign%20on%20their%20headquarters%20on%20February%207.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b392ceeb4be2fff9a4d637%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22661%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20worker%20removes%20the%20sign%20at%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development's%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20headquarters%20on%20February%207%2C%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Elon%20Musk%20abruptly%20froze%20the%20agency.%3Cp%3EKayla%20Bartkowski%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Trump%20froze%20USAID%20spending%20to%20put%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20interests%26quot%3B%20first.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20decision%20has%20left%20at%20least%2012%2C700%20Americans%20jobless%2C%20a%20number%20that%20is%20expected%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20North%20Carolina%2C%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20largest%20USAID%20contractors%2C%20hundreds%20have%20been%20furloughed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20chosen%20to%20delay%20discretionary%20spending%20for%20new%20furniture%20and%20subscription%20services.%20They%20worry%20about%20being%20able%20to%20afford%20groceries%20for%20their%20families.%20And%20they%20have%20been%20left%20to%20wonder%20if%20they%20will%20get%20paid%20for%20work%20already%20performed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E's%20January%2020%20executive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.federalregister.gov%2Fdocuments%2F2025%2F01%2F30%2F2025-02091%2Freevaluating-and-realigning-united-states-foreign-aid%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorder%3C%2Fa%3E%20placed%20a%2090-day%20freeze%20on%20foreign%20aid%20in%20the%20name%20of%20putting%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20interests%26quot%3B%20first.%20That%20order%20and%20other%20actions%2C%20which%20halted%20work%20on%20hundreds%20of%20projects%20funded%20by%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%2C%20known%20as%20USAID%2C%20have%20had%20profound%20ripple%20effects%20on%20American%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntended%20to%20reduce%20wasteful%20spending%20and%20limit%20the%20money%20the%20US%20sends%20overseas%2C%20the%20actions%20have%20impacted%20thousands%20of%20American%20workers%20whose%20jobs%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musk-usaid-ukraine-middle-east-foreign-aid-aids-vaccinations-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efunded%20by%20USAID%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20funding%20freeze%20has%20been%20acutely%20felt%20in%20North%20Carolina%2C%20one%20of%20the%20top%20state%20recipients%20of%20USAID%20dollars%2C%20according%20to%20interviews%20with%20USAID%20contractors%20who%20have%20been%20furloughed%20or%20fired%20with%20little%20information%20about%20whether%20invoices%20for%20past%20work%20will%20be%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20has%20implications%20for%20US%20farmers%2C%20furniture%20makers%2C%20airline%20carriers%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20other%20US%20organizations%20that%20sell%20products%20or%20services%20to%20the%20government%20agency.%20In%20fact%2C%20USAID%20rules%20require%20a%20range%20of%20purchases%20%E2%80%94%20from%20food%20to%20vehicles%20to%20pharmaceuticals%20and%20plane%20tickets%20%E2%80%94%20to%20prioritize%20US%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForeign%20aid%2C%20with%20a%20few%20exceptions%20for%20close%20allies%20such%20as%20Egypt%2C%20Israel%2C%20and%20Jordan%2C%20is%20not%20transferred%20into%20the%20treasuries%20of%20aid%20recipient%20governments%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Natsios%2C%20a%20former%20administrator%20of%20USAID%2C%20said%20in%20February%2013%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2F119%2Fmeeting%2Fhouse%2F117889%2Fwitnesses%2FHHRG-119-FA00-Wstate-NatsiosA-20250213.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etestimony%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20Congress.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20it%20is%20spent%20through%20international%20and%20local%20non-governmental%20organizations%2C%20US%20and%20local%20universities%2C%20for-profit%20development%20contractors%2C%20and%20civil%20society%20organizations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20now%2C%20USAID%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusaid-staff-put-on-administrative-leave-friday-midnight-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaintained%20a%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20around%2010%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Congressional%20Research%20Service%2C%20relying%20on%20contractors%20to%20do%20the%20bulk%20of%20its%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20administration's%20decision%20to%20defund%20USAID%20%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1886307316804263979%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20this%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bspent%20the%20weekend%20feeding%20USAID%20into%20the%20wood%20chipper%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20has%20led%20to%20the%20layoff%20or%20termination%20of%20thousands%20of%20US%20employees%20at%20companies%20that%20contract%20with%20USAID%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usaidstopwork.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSAID%20tracker%3C%2Fa%3E%20set%20up%20by%20Molloy%20Consultants%2C%20a%20global%20health%20consulting%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20and%20the%20State%20Department%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20about%20the%20impact%20on%20US%20workers.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20trying%20to%20be%20disruptive%20to%20people's%20personal%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20said%20on%20February%207.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20being%20punitive%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Marocco%2C%20deputy%20administrator%20for%20USAID%2C%20said%20in%20a%20February%2010%20affidavit%20that%20the%20pause%20was%20necessary%20in%20order%20to%20enable%20%26quot%3Ba%20thorough%20review%20of%20USAID's%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222719a9fc-497c-4039-ad8b-29fce2363b50%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENorth%20Carolina%20takes%20a%20hit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20the%20funding%20freeze%20was%20immediate%20in%20North%20Carolina%2C%20one%20of%20the%20top%20state%20recipients%20of%20USAID%20dollars.%20The%20state%20is%20home%20to%20organizations%20that%20received%20more%20than%20%242.2%20billion%20from%20USAID%2C%20according%20to%20Molloy%20Consultants%2C%20placing%20it%20fifth%20among%20US%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20be%20very%20blunt.%20The%20freeze%20has%20been%20devastating%2C%26quot%3B%20Brianna%20Clarke-Schwelm%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20North%20Carolina%20Global%20Health%20Alliance%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAlready%20we%20are%20seeing%20mass%20furloughs%20and%20mass%20layoffs.%20Hundreds%20of%20people%20have%20already%20lost%20their%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20%26quot%3Bwill%20reach%20people%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20our%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20Carolina%20is%20Trump%20country%3B%20the%20president%20won%20the%20state%20in%202016%2C%202020%2C%20and%202024%2C%20and%20he%20visited%20it%20at%20least%2011%20times%20during%20last%20year's%20campaign%2C%20more%20than%20almost%20any%20other%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenators%20Thom%20Tillis%20and%20Ted%20Budd%2C%20both%20Republicans%2C%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%20Both%20senators%20have%20fielded%20calls%20and%20emails%20from%20constituents%2C%20often%20responding%20with%20impersonal%20emails%2C%20according%20to%20some%20recipients%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20government%20has%20a%20responsibility%20to%20review%20every%20taxpayer%20dollar%20and%20ensure%20that%20it%20is%20spent%20wisely%20and%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20the%20American%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20Budd's%20emails%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentative%20Valerie%20Foushee%2C%20a%20Democrat%20whose%20district%20includes%20Durham%2C%20said%20she%20had%20heard%20from%20hundreds%20of%20constituents%20concerned%20about%20the%20funding%20freeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20deeply%20concerned%20regarding%20the%20illegal%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20Trump%20Administration%20to%20dismantle%20our%20leading%20foreign%20aid%20agency%2C%26quot%3B%20Foushee%20said%20by%20email.%20%26quot%3BTrump's%20detrimental%20Stop%20Work%20Order%20will%20have%20widespread%20repercussions%20across%20our%20state%2C%20affecting%20farmers%2C%20local%20businesses%2C%20researchers%2C%20medical%20professionals%2C%20biotech%20companies%2C%20and%20many%20others.%20In%20my%20district%20alone%2C%20thousands%20of%20workers%20across%20numerous%20international%20development%20organizations%20will%20be%20affected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20Carolina's%20Raleigh-Durham%20metro%20area%20is%20home%20to%20two%20of%20the%20six%20largest%20global%20recipients%20of%20USAID%20funds%20between%202013%20and%202022%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcrsreports.congress.gov%2Fproduct%2Fpdf%2FR%2FR48150%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Congressional%20Research%20Service.%20FHI%20360%2C%20a%20Durham-based%20nonprofit%20focused%20on%20health%2C%20nutrition%2C%20and%20economic%20opportunity%2C%20received%20%243.79%20billion%20during%20those%20years%20and%20RTI%20International%2C%20a%20research%20institution%20based%20in%20Research%20Triangle%20Park%2C%20took%20in%20%242.31%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20February%206%2C%20FHI%20360%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fhi360.org%2Fnews%2Ffhi-360-announces-u-s-staff-furloughs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20would%20furlough%2036%25%20of%20its%20US%20staff%2C%20including%20200%20in%20North%20Carolina.%20Spokesperson%20Jennifer%20Garcia%20declined%20to%20elaborate%20on%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20week%20later%2C%20RTI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org%2Fnews%2Frti-international-announces-temporary-staff-layoffs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisclosed%3C%2Fa%3E%20temporary%20layoffs%20for%20226%20of%20its%20staff%2C%20including%2061%20in%20North%20Carolina.%20%26quot%3BRTI%20deeply%20values%20every%20staff%20member%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Tim%20Gabel%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BThe%20projects%20our%20international%20development%20staff%20implement%20provide%20essential%20contributions%20that%20support%20America's%20leadership%20in%20creating%20a%20more%20prosperous%2C%20safe%2C%20secure%20and%20resilient%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20others%20among%20the%20top%20organizations%20receiving%20USAID%20funds%2C%20Chemonics%20and%20DAI%2C%20also%20employ%20workers%20in%20the%20state.%20Chemonics%20has%20furloughed%20600%20staff%20and%20placed%20another%20300%20on%20limited%20work%20hours%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2025%2F02%2F04%2Fpolitics%2Fusaid-cuts-thousands-american-jobs%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20spokesperson%20told%20CNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20DAI%20furloughed%20about%20380%20staff%2C%2060%20to%2070%25%20of%20their%20workforce%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Monday%2C%20at%20least%2012%2C700%20contractors%20who%20relied%20on%20USAID%20funding%20had%20been%20furloughed%20or%20put%20on%20leave%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usaidstopwork.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enumbers%20compiled%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Molloy%20Consultants%20from%20impacted%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20health%20industry%20is%20a%20significant%20driver%20of%20North%20Carolina's%20economy.%20The%20industry%20accounted%20for%20roughly%20170%2C000%20jobs%20in%20the%20state%20and%20added%20almost%20%2432%20billion%20in%20value%20to%20the%20state's%20economy%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncglobalhealth.org%2F_files%2Fugd%2F6acda1_0544a60a3d3643a1b789e8d1a0206495.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20commissioned%20by%20NCGHA.%20That's%20about%204%25%20of%20the%20state's%20GDP%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20jobs%20or%20been%20furloughed%2C%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20have%20been%20traumatic.%20Many%20told%20BI%20they%20are%20applying%20for%20unemployment%20benefits.%20One%20person%20decided%20to%20cancel%20plans%20to%20buy%20a%20new%20North%20Carolina-made%20couch%20after%20being%20put%20on%20furlough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20folks%20realize%20how%20big%20of%20an%20industry%20this%20is%20for%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20person%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20to%20avoid%20professional%20repercussions.%20%26quot%3BJust%20in%20the%20Triangle%20you%20have%20two%20of%20the%20largest%20implementers%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20then%20countless%20NGOs%20impacted.%20Multiply%20that%20by%2049%20states.%20How%20many%20jobs%20are%20we%20talking%20about%20here%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20April%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20said%20it%20would%20spend%20%241%20billion%20to%20buy%20US%20commodities%20for%20USAID%20to%20ship%20overseas.%20A%20USAID%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F679bdd21823c9474a907e5b3%2Ft%2F67aa49892462b91f2c032559%2F1739213201516%2FNorth%2BCarolina%2BUSAID.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efact%20sheet%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20the%20agency%20partnered%20with%20at%20least%2027%20North%20Carolina%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%20businesses%20have%20also%20been%20impacted.%20In%20December%2C%20a%20government%20official%20said%20the%20agency%20sent%20%241%20billion%20to%20US%20small%20businesses%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupport%20for%20small%20firms%20has%20included%20State%20Department%20purchases%20of%20at%20least%20%247.5%20million%20furniture%20over%20the%20last%20eight%20years%20from%20North%20Carolina%20manufacturers%20to%20fill%20embassies%2C%20missions%2C%20residences%2C%20and%20USAID%20facilities%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usaspending.gov%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusaspending.gov%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20continues%2C%2090%25%20of%20the%20NGO%20and%20contractor%20community%20will%20cease%20to%20exist%20within%20another%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Natsio%20said%20in%20his%20testimony%20last%20week.%20%26quot%3BNGOs%2C%20many%20of%20them%20faith-based%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevangelical-leaders-respond-donald-trump-usaid-foreign-aid-cuts-doge-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristian%20organizations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20shut%20down%20programs%2C%20lay%20off%20staff%20(which%20many%20have%20already%20been%20forced%20to%20do)%2C%20and%20ultimately%20close%20their%20doors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USAID%20spending%20freeze%20has%20also%20affected%20the%20state's%20universities%2C%20as%20the%20University%20of%20North%20Carolina%20system%2C%20North%20Carolina%20State%20University%2C%20North%20Carolina%20A%26amp%3BT%20State%20University%2C%20and%20Duke%20University%20had%20all%20received%20USAID%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20University%20of%20North%20Carolina%20at%20Chapel%20Hill's%20Carolina%20Population%20Center%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cpc.unc.edu%2Fnews%2Func-awarded-90-million-global-health-pearl-project-to-support-localized-generation-and-use-of-evidence-and-data%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceived%20a%20%2490%20million%20grant%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20USAID%20to%20monitor%20global%20health.%20Between%202003%20and%202015%2C%20the%20center's%20Measure%20Evaluation%20program%20received%20an%20additional%20%24500%20million%20from%20USAID%20to%20handle%20data%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUNC%20Chapel%20Hill%20has%2010%20stop%20work%20orders%20from%20USAID%2C%20including%20three%20in%20which%20the%20university%20is%20a%20direct%20recipient%20and%20another%20seven%20in%20which%20it%20is%20a%20subrecipient%2C%20spokesperson%20Cat%20Long%20said%20by%20email.%20The%20university%20had%20received%20%2418.3%20million%20in%20research%20awards%20this%20fiscal%20year%20and%20%2417.5%20million%20in%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20University%20is%20awaiting%20more%20information%20from%20federal%20agencies%20to%20determine%20the%20long-term%20impact%20on%20these%20programs%20and%20their%20staff%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENC%20State%20%26quot%3Bis%20working%20with%20various%20partners%20to%20gauge%20potential%20impacts%20of%20any%20changes%20to%20federally%20funded%20sponsored%20programs%2C%26quot%3B%20university%20spokesperson%20Mick%20Kulikowski%20said%20by%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChemonics%2C%20DAI%2C%20and%20the%20Small%20Business%20Association%20for%20International%20Companies%2C%20a%20Raleigh-based%20trade%20association%20with%20more%20than%20150%20members%2C%20were%20among%20eight%20plaintiffs%20who%20filed%20suit%20on%20February%2011%20to%20challenge%20the%20administration's%20freeze.%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20issued%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musk-doge-usaid-shutdown-blocked-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etemporary%20restraining%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20giving%20the%20administration%20five%20days%20to%20restart%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrganizations%20representing%20USAID%20workers%20have%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusaid-employment-cut-foreign-aid-trump-rubio-lawsuit-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20suit%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20uncertainty%20reigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20staff%20member%20at%20one%20of%20the%20major%20North%20Carolina%20organizations%20funded%20by%20USAID%20said%20organizations%20still%20don't%20know%20if%20invoices%20for%20work%20performed%20in%20November%2C%20December%2C%20and%20January%20will%20be%20paid.%20Another%20said%20that%20organizations%20are%20furloughing%20staff%20simply%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20any%20cash%20on%20hand%20to%20pay%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20furloughed%20employees%20of%20USAID%20contractors%20said%20that%20their%20projects%20are%20heavily%20audited%2C%20and%20they%20pushed%20back%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20there%20is%20widespread%20wasteful%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successfully%20audited%20organizations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20person%20who'd%20been%20furloughed.%20%26quot%3BMonitoring%20and%20evaluation%20is%20such%20a%20big%20part%20of%20every%20project.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20work%20for%20USAID%2C%20a%20USAID%20contractor%2C%20or%20another%20government%20agency%20affected%20by%20furloughs%2C%20please%20contact%20Dakin%20Campbell%20at%20dcampbell%40insider.com%20or%20text%20him%20securely%20at%20dakin.11%20on%20the%20Signal%20app.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-e