rget%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJustAnswer%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20become%20popular%20as%20people%20look%20for%20additional%20income.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20David%20C.%20Bond%20develops%20a%20longer-term%20career%20project%2C%20he's%20doing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-started-on-justanswer-an-antiques-appraisal-site-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egig%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20taps%20his%20expertise%20in%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20early%202023%2C%20Bond%20has%20worked%20for%20JustAnswer%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20connects%20users%20with%20questions%20to%20experts%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewho%20can%20try%20to%20help.%20Many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanswering-questions-justanswer-expert-advice-rv-motorhome-online-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equestions%20he%20answers%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20about%20the%20value%20and%20authenticity%20of%20art%20and%20antiques.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20earned%20almost%20%2443%2C000%2C%20and%20last%20year%2C%20he%20earned%20a%20little%20over%20%2447%2C000.%20He%20said%20the%20gig%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20and%20that%20it's%20been%20difficult%20to%20grow%20his%20earnings%2C%20but%20that%20it's%20provided%20a%20valuable%20income%20stream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJustAnswer%20is%20simultaneously%20fun%20and%20frustrating%2C%26quot%3B%20Bond%2C%2061%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20Bond%20has%20been%20paid%20between%20%247.50%20and%20%2411.50%20per%20question%2C%20a%20rate%20that%20is%20set%20by%20the%20platform.%20Bond%20said%20fluctuations%20in%20his%20pay%20rate%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20pay%20rate%20growth%20over%20time%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20frustrating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustAnswer%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20payouts%20vary%20by%20factors%20including%20geography%2C%20field%2C%20prior%20success%20in%20helping%20customers%2C%20and%20sup