m%20Shadows%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shadow%20that%20was%20cast%20over%20Saudi%20and%20its%20de%20facto%20leader%2C%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%2C%20after%20the%20murder%20of%20the%20Saudi%20journalist%20Jamal%20Khashoggi%20in%202018%20in%20Turkey%20seems%20to%20be%20lifting%2C%20although%20there%20are%20still%20concerns%20over%20the%20country's%20human%20rights%20record.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20historic%20ally%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20avoided%20choosing%20sides%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20The%20world's%20leading%20exporter%20of%20crude%20oil%20maintains%20close%20relations%20with%20Russia%20on%20energy%20policy%20while%20promising%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kingdom%20has%20been%20enhancing%20its%20role%20diplomatically%20and%20during%20the%20Biden%20era%2C%20it%20pivoted%20away%20from%20reliance%20on%20the%20US%20as%20its%20key%20international%20ally%20by%20striking%20closer%20ties%20with%20America's%20rivals%20like%20Russia%20and%20China.%20The%20Saudis%20have%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20would%20follow%20what%20they%20perceive%20as%20their%20interests%20first%20and%20foremost%2C%20a%20move%20more%20conducive%20to%20the%20transactional%20nature%20of%20Mr%20Trump's%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump's%20first%20foreign%20visit%20in%20his%20first%20term%20was%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20and%20the%20Kingdom%20has%20welcomed%20his%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20possible%20reasons%20for%20Mr%20Trump%20to%20keep%20Riyadh%20close%20could%20be%20a%20smooth%20culmination%20of%20the%20Abraham%20Accords%20that%20he%20initiated%20in%20his%20first%20term.%20However%2C%20war%20in%20Gaza%20has%20subsequently%20got%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20deal%20and%20may%20well%20raise%20the%20price%20that%20Saudi%20Arabia%20will%20demand%20for%20a%20peace%20agreement%20with%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Big%20Coup%20For%20Saudi'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20big%20coup%20for%20Saudi.%20The%20two%20superpowers%20come%20to%20Riyadh%20to%20settle%20their%20disagreements%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ali%20Shihabi%2C%20an%20advisor%20to%20the%20Saudi%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20quite%20prestigious%20and%20affirms%20the%20soft%20power%20of%20the%20kingdom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiyadh%20will%20then%20play%20host%20to%20an%20Arab%20summit%20on%20Friday%20to%20discuss%20the%20response%20to%20Trump's%20proposal%20for%20a%20US%20takeover%20of%20Gaza%20and%20the%20forced%20displacement%20of%20its%20more%20than%20two%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20six%20member%20states%20of%20the%20Gulf%20Cooperation%20Council%20(GCC)%20will%20attend%2C%20as%20will%20those%20of%20Egypt%20and%20Jordan%2C%20which%20Trump%20has%20floated%20as%20possible%20destinations%20for%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia's%20entry%20into%20the%20spotlight%20comes%20after%20the%20oil-rich%20power%20watched%20its%20smaller%20neighbour%20Qatar%20mediate%20a%20hard-won%20yet%20fragile%20truce%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSaudi%20Arabia%20has%20been%20able%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20contradictions%20and%20the%20confrontation%20between%20the%20West%20and%20Russia%20in%20the%20Ukrainian%20crisis%2C%20particularly%20on%20the%20oil%20issue%2C%20without%20losing%20any%20of%20its%20allies%2C%20whether%20Western%20or%20Russian%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rabha%20Seif%20Allam%20of%20the%20Al-Ahram%20Center%20for%20Political%20and%20Strategic%20Studies%20in%20Cairo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20helped%20to%20bring%20it%20out%20of%20the%20isolation%20imposed%20on%20it%20after%20the%20Khashoggi%20affair%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussia-US%20Talks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20of%20US%20and%20Russian%20officials%20comes%20after%20three%20years%20of%20an%20almost%20total%20freeze%20in%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20over%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20European%20leaders%20met%20in%20Paris%20on%20Monday%20to%20discuss%20their%20strategy%2C%20while%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20is%20expected%20in%20Turkey%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Riyadh%2C%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%2C%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Mike%20Waltz%20and%20Special%20Envoy%20for%20the%20Middle%20East%20Steve%20Witkoff%20met%20with%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20on%20Monday.%20Russian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20and%20Yuri%20Ushakov%2C%20Putin's%20diplomatic%20adviser%2C%20were%20dispatched%20to%20the%20Saudi%20capital%20to%20meet%20with%20their%20American%20counterparts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20between%20the%20two%20teams%20%26quot%3Bis%20immensely%20significant%20from%20a%20Saudi%20perspective%20as%20it%20raises%20its%20stature%20in%20world%20diplomacy%20and%20as%20a%20responsible%20global%20actor%20ready%20to%20contribute%20towards%20global%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Umer%20Karim%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20Saudi%20foreign%20policy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20meeting%20indicates%20that%20Saudi%20leadership%20and%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20in%20particular%20has%20developed%20a%20cordial%20close%20and%20very%20personal%20relationship%20with%20both%20President%20Trump%20and%20Putin%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Birmingham%20academic%20said%20the%20Saudi%20crown%20prince%20had%20much%20to%20gain%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Bdiplomatic%20activity%26quot%3B%20in%20Riyadh%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bbecoming%20a%20crucial%20actor%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20world%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739865840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F934q1dcg_marco-rubio-saudi-afp_625x300_18_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-donald-trump-chose-saudi-arabia-as-venue-for-ukraine-talks-7737020%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20top%20diplomats%20of%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Russia%20are%20making%20their%20way%20over%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20hold%20key%20talks%20on%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-donald-trump-chose-saudi-arabia-as-venue-for-ukraine-talks-7737020%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20passengers%20survive%20crash%20landing%20as%20plane%20flips%20at%20Toronto%20airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739865626000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F80bf%2Flive%2F6fea39f0-eda6-11ef-a819-277e390a7a08.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc20g02djlv7o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eighteen%20of%20the%2080%20people%20on%20board%20were%20injured%20after%20the%20Delta%20plane%20overturned%20on%20landing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A359%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc20g02djlv7o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc20g02djlv7o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc20g02djlv7o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Embassy's%20Message%20To%20Nepali%20Students%20After%20KIIT%20Student%20Death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Nepal%20assured%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20the%20alleged%20suicide%20of%20a%20Nepal%20woman%20student%20at%20Odisha's%20Kalinga%20Institute%20of%20Industrial%20Technology%20(KIIT)%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20return%20to%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakriti%20Lamsal%2C%20a%20third-year%20B%20Tech%20student%20of%20the%20Bhubaneswar-based%20institute%2C%20died%20allegedly%20by%20suicide%20at%20her%20hostel%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20incident%20triggered%20protests%20on%20the%20campus%2C%20where%20around%201%2C000%20Nepali%20students%20study.%20Students%20shouted%20slogans%2C%20blocked%20roads%20and%20pushed%20through%20the%20gates%20of%20buildings.%20A%20male%20student%20has%20been%20taken%20into%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20Nepalese%20students%20also%20staged%20a%20demonstration%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20Kathmandu%20with%20placards%20demanding%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20embassy%20said%20that%20KIIT%20has%20appealed%20to%20Nepali%20students%20to%20%26quot%3Breturn%20to%20the%20campus%2C%20resume%20their%20classes%2C%20and%20stay%20in%20the%20hostels%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BNepali%20students%20studying%20in%20India%20form%20an%20important%20facet%20of%20the%20enduring%20people%20to%20people%20links%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20The%20Government%20of%20India%20will%20continue%20to%20take%20all%20necessary%20steps%20to%20ensure%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20Nepali%20students%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20situation%20escalated%20on%20campus%20amid%20protests%2C%20KIIT%20authorities%20had%20allegedly%20evicted%20several%20Nepali%20students%20from%20the%20hostel%20and%20dropped%20them%20at%20Cuttack%20railway%20station%20without%20making%20any%20arrangements%20for%20their%20travel.%20The%20institute%20later%20clarified%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20administration%20made%20extensive%20efforts%2C%20engaging%20in%20counseling%20and%20discussions%20for%20over%2010%20hours%20to%20manage%20the%20situation%20peacefully.%20However%2C%20despite%20their%20best%20attempts%2C%20some%20protestors%20were%20unwilling%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20university%20authorities%20and%20continued%20to%20create%20disruptions%2C%20posing%20a%20challenge%20to%20law%20and%20order.%20They%20also%20blocked%20the%20main%20road%20for%20hours%2C%20causing%20inconvenience%20and%20escalating%20tensions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20further%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BTo%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20and%20unbiased%20investigation%2C%20Nepali%20students%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20return%20to%20their%20respective%20places%20with%20the%20help%20of%20local%20guardians%20until%20the%20inquiry%20is%20completed.%20Their%20academic%20aspects%20will%20not%20be%20disturbed%20during%20this%20period%20and%20will%20be%20taken%20care%20of%20by%20the%20university.%26quot%3B%20To%20maintain%20order%20on%20the%20campus%2C%20two%20platoons%20(each%20platoon%20consisting%20of%2030%20personnel)%20of%20police%20were%20deployed.%20Police%20also%20sealed%20the%20Ms%20Lamsal's%20room%20and%20kept%20her%20body%20in%20the%20mortuary%20until%20her%20parents%20arrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Lamsal's%20father%20alleged%20that%20the%20private%20engineering%20institute%20%26quot%3Bmistreated%26quot%3B%20undergraduates%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20country.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20lost%20my%20daughter.%20Many%20other%20children%20are%20studying%20here.%20It%20is%20known%20from%20the%20media%20that%20some%20students%20were%20driven%20out%20of%20their%20hostel.%20This%20is%20not%20right.%20This%20incident%20should%20not%20be%20repeated.%20These%20people%20go%20to%20Nepal%20and%20invite%20students%20to%20study%20here.%20The%20institute%20mistreated%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunil%20Lamsal%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20higher%20education%20minister%20Suryabanshi%20Suraj%20said%20the%20government%20has%20directed%20the%20university%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20Nepali%20students%20to%20Bhubaneswar%20by%20special%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKIIT%20also%20assured%20that%20academic%20losses%20of%20students%20will%20be%20take%20care%20of%20by%20the%20institute.%20It%20set%20up%20a%2024%2F7%20control%20room%20at%20its%20campus%206%20to%20assist%20Nepali%20students%20returning%20to%20the%20university.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20KIIT%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20dedicated%20control%20room%20is%20open%2024x7%20at%20KIIT%20Campus%206%20to%20facilitate%20the%20return%20of%20Nepali%20students%20to%20the%20KIIT%20campus.%20Additionally%2C%20a%2024x7%20helpline%20%5B%2B91%207847064550%20%26amp%3B%20%2B91%207855029322%5D%20has%20been%20set%20up%20to%20provide%20support%20and%20guidance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Nepal's%20Prime%20Minister%20K%20P%20Sharma%20Oli%20said%20two%20officers%20had%20been%20sent%20to%20counsel%20the%20students%2C%20with%20arrangements%20made%20to%20offer%20them%20the%20options%20of%20staying%20in%20their%20hostel%20or%20returning%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20nearest%20mental%20health%20specialist.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739865420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fkme1oljg_kiit-students_625x300_17_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-embassys-message-to-nepali-students-after-kiit-student-death-7736976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Nepal%20assured%20tho