thout-going-to-gym-centenarians-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Caught%20red-handed%20and%20...'%3A%20Cognizant%20in%20court%20filing%20against%20Infosys%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739864842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118350872%2Cimgsize-785816.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fcaught-red-handed-and-cognizant-in-court-filing-against-infosys%2Farticleshow%2F118350897.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cognizant%20has%20accused%20Infosys%20of%20stealing%20trade%20secrets%20related%20to%20its%20TriZetto%20healthcare%20software%2C%20claiming%20Infosys%20unlawfully%20used%20its%20data%20and%20refused%20an%20audit.%20This%20allegation%20follows%20Infosys%20counter-suing%20Cognizant%20for%20anti-competitive%20tactics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20Hours%2C%204%20Trains%2C%20Mega%20Crowd%3A%20Sources%20On%20What%20Caused%20Delhi%20Stampede%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20into%20the%20deadly%20stampede%20at%20New%20Delhi%20railway%20station%20on%20Saturday%2C%20which%20killed%2018%20-%20including%20five%20children%20-%20has%20revealed%20that%20a%20senior%20Railway%20Police%20Force%20(RPF)%20official%20had%20asked%20the%20station%20manager%20not%20to%20issue%20any%20more%20tickets%20after%20he%20sensed%20that%20the%20crowd%20had%20become%20too%20large%20and%20an%20uncontrollable%20situation%20could%20arise%2C%20but%20thousands%20were%20already%20on%20the%20platforms%20by%20then%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERailway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20extraordinary%20rush%20at%20the%20station.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20an%20RPF%20investigation%20report%20into%20the%20incident%20found%20that%20four%20trains%20to%20Prayagraj%20were%20scheduled%20to%20leave%20the%20New%20Delhi%20railway%20station%20between%208.15%20pm%20and%2010.10%20pm%20-%20a%20span%20of%20just%20two%20hours%20-%20resulting%20in%20a%20massive%20crowd%20of%20Maha%20Kumbh%20devotees%20descending%20on%20the%20platforms.%20Reports%20had%20said%20that%2C%20on%20average%2C%20nearly%201%2C500%20general%20tickets%20were%20sold%20at%20the%20station%20every%20hour%20and%20many%20more%20were%20purchased%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RPF%20report%20said%20that%20the%20Shiv%20Ganga%20Express%2C%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Varanasi%20via%20Prayagraj%2C%20was%20scheduled%20to%20depart%20from%20platform%20number%2012%20at%208.15%20pm%2C%20the%20Magadh%20Express%20to%20West%20Bengal's%20Islampur%20via%20Prayagraj%20from%20platform%20number%2014%20at%209%20pm%20and%20the%20Prayagraj%20Express%20from%20the%20same%20platform%20at%2010.10%20pm.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20Shiv%20Ganga%20Express%20left%2C%20thousands%20of%20passengers%20could%20not%20make%20it%20on%20the%20crowded%20train%20and%20that's%20when%20they%20found%20out%20that%20a%20special%20train%20would%20leave%20for%20Prayagraj%20from%20platform%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sparked%20a%20frenzy%20and%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20the%20big%20mass%20of%20people%20began%20trying%20to%20make%20its%20way%20from%20platform%2012%20to%2016%20to%20board%20the%20special%20train%20using%20foot%20overbridges%20two%20and%20three.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20usual%20rush%2C%20a%20crowd%20of%20people%20was%20already%20heading%20for%20platform%2014%20for%20the%20two%20trains%20to%20Prayagraj%20and%20the%20overflow%20from%20platform%2012%20joined%20this%20throng.%20This%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20led%20to%20the%20stampede.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20mentions%20that%20when%20the%20crowd%20began%20to%20swell%20to%20a%20point%20that%20the%20situation%20seemed%20to%20be%20h