it%20a%20try%20and%20found%20it%20to%20be%20highly%20effective%20for%20her%20own%20farm%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20Narendra%2009%20wheat%20special%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20son%20farm%20the%20wheat%20on%20six%20acres%20of%20land.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20difference%20in%20the%20variety%20of%20wheat%20is%20that%20we%20see%20each%20acre%20producing%202%2C800%20to%202%2C900%20kgs%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F393883%2Fchokhone-krichena-dianthe-floriculture-mao-manipur-empowering-farmer%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommercial%20farming%20practices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20significantly%20more%20than%20most%20crops%20grown%20in%20the%20region.%20We%20grow%20them%20organically%20as%20well%2C%20and%20there%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20produce%20is%20better%20than%20many%20others%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20wheat%20variety%20required%20significantly%20less%20water%20than%20traditional%20crops%2C%20making%20it%20especially%20beneficial%20in%20water-scarce%20areas.%20With%20yields%20reaching%201%2C800%20to%202%2C000%20kg%20per%20acre%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%202%2C500%20kg%2C%20it%20quickly%20became%20a%20sought-after%20crop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20time%20passed%2C%20people%20who%20received%20these%20grains%20started%20to%20sow%20them%2C%20and%20after%20getting%20good%20results%2C%20they%20started%20talking%20about%20them.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20story%20began%2C%20and%20Mehra%20decided%20to%20take%20his%20discovery%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20time%2C%20he%20realised%20the%20harm%20these%20chemicals%20were%20causing%20to%20the%20soil%2C%20crops%2C%20and%20food.%20Mehra%20gradually%20learnt%20more%20about%20sustainable%20farming%20practices%20and%20decided%20to%20make%20it%20a%20part%20of%20his%20life